PewterCity_Gym_Text_BrockIntro::
    .string "Hi there! I'm FARIS.\n"
    .string "I'm the LEADER of the STEVENAGE GYM.\p"
    .string "I believe in the power of the mind\n"
    .string "and the magic of friendship!\p"
    .string "Are you ready to see what my\n"
    .string "POKéMON can do?\p"
    .string "Let's have a great match!{PLAY_BGM}{MUS_ENCOUNTER_GYM_LEADER}$"

PewterCity_Gym_Text_BrockDefeat::
    .string "Wow! You're really amazing!\p"
    .string "As proof of your victory, please\n"
    .string "take the BOULDERBADGE.\p"
    .string "{FONT_NORMAL}{PLAYER} received the BOULDERBADGE\n"
    .string "from FARIS!{PAUSE_MUSIC}{PLAY_BGM}{MUS_OBTAIN_BADGE}{PAUSE 0xFE}{PAUSE 0x56}{RESUME_MUSIC}\p"
    .string "{FONT_MALE}That badge is a symbol of your\n"
    .string "strength and determination.$"

PewterCity_Gym_Text_TakeThisWithYou::
    .string "Wait!\n"
    .string "Take this with you.$"

PewterCity_Gym_Text_ReceivedTM39FromBrock::
    .string "{PLAYER} received TM39\n"
    .string "from FARIS.$"

PewterCity_Gym_Text_ExplainTM39::
    .string "A TM, Technical Machine, contains a\n"
    .string "technique for POKéMON.\p"
    .string "Using a TM teaches the move it\n"
    .string "contains to a POKéMON.\p"
    .string "A TM is good for only one use.\p"
    .string "So, when you use one, pick the\n"
    .string "POKéMON carefully.\p"
    .string "Anyways…\n"
    .string "TM39 contains ROCK TOMB.\p"
    .string "It hurls boulders at the foe and\n"
    .string "lowers its SPEED.$"

PewterCity_Gym_Text_BrockPostBattle::
    .string "You have a bright future ahead of\n"
    .string "you as a TRAINER.\p"
    .string "Keep believing in yourself and\n"
    .string "your POKéMON!\p"
    .string "Why don't you head to LETCHWORTH\n"
    .string "next? BRYONY will be happy to\l"
    .string "see you!$"

PewterCity_Gym_Text_DontHaveRoomForThis::
    .string "You don't have room for this.$"

PewterCity_Gym_Text_LiamIntro::
    .string "Stop right there, kid!\p"
    .string "You're not ready to face FARIS yet!$"

PewterCity_Gym_Text_LiamDefeat::
    .string "Darn!\p"
    .string "Light-years isn't time…\n"
    .string "It measures distance!$"

PewterCity_Gym_Text_LiamPostBattle::
    .string "You're good, but FARIS is on a\n"
    .string "whole other level!$"

PewterCity_Gym_Text_OllieIntro::
    .string "OLLIE: Hey SHUKTI! I'm watching you...\n"
    .string "you're doing great.\p"
    .string "I've got a little something for you.\n"
    .string "It reminded me of us.$"

PewterCity_Gym_Text_OllieGiftPewter::
    .string "OLLIE: Here, take this.$"

PewterCity_Gym_Text_OllieAdvice::
    .string "OLLIE: FARIS uses Psychic and Fairy\n"
    .string "types. They're strong, but they\l"
    .string "can't hide from what's coming.\p"
    .string "I'll be waiting for you at the\n"
    .string "very end, Shukti.$"

PewterCity_Gym_Text_OlliePostVictory::
    .string "OLLIE: Just as I thought!\n"
    .string "You're POKéMON champ material!\p"
    .string "I'm already at the summit, waiting\n"
    .string "for our final date with destiny.$"

PewterCity_Gym_Text_NoRoomForGift::
    .string "OLLIE: Oh, your BAG is full!\n"
    .string "I'll hold onto this for you.$"

